"  / for commands                                     ! for shell commands       "
"  shift + enter for newline                          tab to queue message       "
"  @ for file paths                                   ctrl + v to paste images   "
"  ctrl + g to edit in external editor                esc again to edit previous "
"  ctrl + r search history                            ctrl + x then ctrl + u to u"
"  ctrl + x then ctrl + y to copy last output         ctrl + x then ctrl + r to r"
"  ctrl + c to exit                                                              "
"  ctrl + t to view transcript                                                   "
